{"type": "article", "id": 25514, "title": "Dior销售大涨，以及，霉霉在VOGUE拍的大片不太像她｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-15T09:40:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 20492, "name": "佛罗伦萨男装展"}, {"id": 23146, "name": "杂志封面"}, {"id": 26292, "name": "五月刊"}, {"id": 605, "name": "小黑裙"}, {"id": 7202, "name": "高管"}, {"id": 883, "name": "创新"}, {"id": 67, "name": "科技"}, {"id": 2898, "name": "M&S"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 24445, "name": "A.P.C"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607190503ESsm6Kor7F4tGXCl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/LVMH-CEO-says-Dior-sales-could-reach-5-bln-eur-this-year,682119.html#rc\"><b>Dior 销售额今年或将超 50 亿欧元</b></a>｜近日，时尚和美容产品的 Dior 品牌，母公司 LVMH 的 CEO Bernard Arnault 在巴黎年会上表示 Dior 今年的总销售额将超过 50 亿欧元（约合 56.3 亿美元）。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/The-Estee-Lauder-Companies-announces-leadership-changes,681999.html#rc\"><b>雅诗兰黛领导层变动</b></a>｜护肤品牌雅诗兰黛周四宣布一系列领导层，其中欧洲、中东和非洲区总裁 Ivan Fernandez 将退休， 8 月 31 日生效，结束其在公司的 25 年职业生涯。由 Peter Jueptner 接任，此前他是集团战略、新业务发展等部门的执行副总裁。Stephane de la Faverie 担任雅诗兰黛全球品牌总裁，Maria Cristina González Noguera 任全球公共事务高级副总裁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/4/14/11431152/vogue-changes-price-increase\"><b>美国版 Vogue 将涨价</b></a>｜ Vogue 的出版人兼首席营收官 Susan Plagemann 近日向时尚媒体 BOF 透露了未来 Vogue 杂志的几个主要变化，首先杂志的开本会由先前的 8 英寸*10 7/8 英寸（约合 20.32 ＊27.6 厘米）扩大到 9 英寸＊10 7/8 英寸，同时杂志的价格将从 5.99 美元（约合人民币 38.8 元）涨至 6.99 美元（45.3 元）。订阅者一年将支付 84 美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Raf-Simons-to-be-surprise-guest-at-Pitti-Uomo,682092.html#rc\"><b>Raf Simons 将再次参加佛罗伦萨男装展</b></a>｜Raf Simons 再次参加佛罗伦萨男装展（Pitti Uomo ），这是他 20 年间第四次参与。自上月 Pitti Uomo 宣布正值 Pitti Uomo  90 周年之际，特邀设计师的名单包括(Gosha Rubchinskiy, Fausto Puglisi, Visvim 和 Lucio Vanotti)，即将在 6 月 14-17 日举办，近日又宣布这位著名设计师前 Dior 创意总监 Raf Simons 也将出席，带来自己的 2017 春夏系列，因此他将不参与巴黎时装周。</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;\">一些值得一看的：</span></h2>\n<p class=\"\">霉霉登 Vogue 五月刊封面，一套写真看起来有点不像她：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190449eOvRbz6jGcSTKCMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190449LyYnwHrBDfzTXkpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190450AmCFolXR6bYakesn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190450SgjsJ1r73oEI5hcQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190451uMUGx1LX4szKdnNP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190451RiTQnvEuPm58zjbw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">A.P.C. 创始人 Jean Touitou 介绍自己设计的一个<a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/4/apc-5-dresses-capsule-collection\">“5 Dresses” 五件小黑裙系列</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190452ps8YZ04HqKDcf3bw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190452b7aApFwiQSmt5kC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190453QsEcLo56MGR97beI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190453kBLi9mIWRrwyahTo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190454XQhlcODfZ90KNW8Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">IT girl “钟小姐” Alexa Chung 穿衣风格一向受到众人喜爱，最近与英国品牌 Mark &amp; Spencer <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/alexa-chung-x-marks-and-spencer/\">推出合作系列 Archive By Alexa</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190454gTy1BvptUbdVOzZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190455msYOxPHWyMRAcTub.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071904555MrpCO819Z3uJnab.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190456fOHIw6J04UVAN5Zm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190457sycFi9Q1pad3fj20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190457E7npCeXPuiABd5Go.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190457NxJbeSscunAC0om8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Bobbi Brown <a href=\"http://popbee.cn/beauty/make-up/bobbi-brown-beach-nude-collection/\">推出夏季限定彩妆</a>，包括三款眼影盘和三款唇膏 Peach Sorbet、Pink Gold、Boho Bronze ，珠光粉色元素为主，6 月 3 日上市：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190458fpqw8exz2l9LtEmV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190458ze2oydXWA5VwIQCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">快到夏天了，毕业季也快来了， Nasty Gal 推出了个<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/nasty-gal-anti-prom-dress-2016-shop/\">“毕业舞会”特别系列</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190459rP9njFoqs6MRNl57.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50187735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190459eJIisS5kuMhtc03T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50187735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190500A1mSCporq75Os8XW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50187735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190500m5ck0eZKWDshanjd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190501zeXfROVdboChNME6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50187735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> Hood By Air 与韩国眼镜品牌 Gentle Monster 推出<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/04/15/hood-by-air-gentle-monster-sunglasses-ss16/#slide-4\">未来感的春夏墨镜系列</a><br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190501dqaHPrguOtKFWcj8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190502i2f9wGjKIzoXqBrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060719050205cnsRGdlbQq6pa4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190502gCis7u6ybxmQTW0R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n\n\n"}